{"tid":1323900,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[老翻都可以收購正版，有錢真係大晒] 網易收購《Dead by Daylight》開發商部分股權","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T13:45:20.000Z","uid":75050,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"38c918d490b56379b5d99844a626d0cbbf340ddf","tid":1323900,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2380617958875378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2380617958875378&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=94edc711\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2380617958875378</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSDVPKD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSDVPKD.png&h=635b7ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【新聞】網易收購《Dead by Daylight》開發商部分股權</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n今天（7月16日）網易在官網發佈公告，確認已經收購了《Dead by Daylight》開發商Behaviour Interactive的部分股權，R&eacute;mi Racine將繼續領導Behaviour Interactive的遊戲開發工作。<br />\n<br />\n網易副總裁Ethan Wang表示，他們非常高興能與Behaviour進一步發展關係，Behaviour是網絡遊戲和非對稱類型遊戲開發的先驅者，網易希望能藉助Behaviour在遊戲開發方面的經驗和實力，推出更多優秀的遊戲作品給各位玩家。<br />\n<br />\nR&eacute;mi Racine同樣表達了對網易非常高的評價，他在聲明中說道&ldquo;網易是網絡遊戲行業的領導者，擁有非常優秀的研發、運營能力和經驗。這次與網易的合作也證明了Behaviour過去21年在網絡遊戲上所建立的聲譽，相信這次合作會推進公司在未來的穩定、持續發展。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n2018年10月網易曾宣布與Behaviour進行戰略合作，《Dead by Daylight》的製作人將作為《第五人格》的遊戲顧問，為《第五人格》的開發和運營提供幫助。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AfMTBpM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAfMTBpM.jpg&h=99c17c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycQk0Rs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FycQk0Rs.png&h=1d803cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ChrgzbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChrgzbB.jpg&h=754e8af2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bd224a585c81cb2dd6fd5c77427a2debcdc72a5","tid":1323900,"uid":69937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"pubg又係咁<br />\nlol又係咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快就到mon hun"},{"pid":"4533510a5202d3e05269bab83ddff640f0e5c35c","tid":1323900,"uid":15810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bd224a585c81cb2dd6fd5c77427a2debcdc72a5","tid":1323900,"uid":69937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"pubg又係咁<br />\nlol又係咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快就到mon hun"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"2013 騰訊出嗰隻Monster Hunter Online已經係<br />\n全球淨係得中國有得玩<br />\n不過capcom 撈咗咁多年，應該無咁易賣股份俾人"},{"pid":"57c5865538f15338a1b33f319d0826f038d0f8b6","tid":1323900,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4533510a5202d3e05269bab83ddff640f0e5c35c","tid":1323900,"uid":15810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bd224a585c81cb2dd6fd5c77427a2debcdc72a5","tid":1323900,"uid":69937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"pubg又係咁<br />\nlol又係咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快就到mon hun"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"2013 騰訊出嗰隻Monster Hunter Online已經係<br />\n全球淨係得中國有得玩<br />\n不過capcom 撈咗咁多年，應該無咁易賣股份俾人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:07:12.000Z","msg":"執左啦"},{"pid":"9fd10cddbdeb9105e8e22ef396cf2df1ffc15077","tid":